Package gw.api.exposure

Class NewExposureMenuItem

java.lang.Object
gw.api.exposure.NewExposureMenuItem
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<NewExposureMenuItem>
public class NewExposureMenuItem extends Object implements Comparable<NewExposureMenuItem>
Represents an item in the new exposure menu. Contains state needed to construct the go() to the NewExposure location.
Author:
akeefer
